<img @src="setup.ImagePath+'icon.png'" class="floatr">\
Now that you've told us your information, it's time to take your picture for our records!

Here, there are a few ways to choose your character's portrait. First, is using an AI model to generate your portrait. That will ensure that no matter what changes you undergo, your portrait can match what you look like. However, that option requires setting up an OpenAI API key and costs around $0.04 per image in API costs. (Unless you're comfortable using a local AI image program to make the images for free)

