Thank you for playing the Twine game adaptation of the Abyss Diver CYOA, developed with love by FloricSpacer.

This was was originally based on the image-CYOA Abyss Diver, with permission of the original author on the condition of their anonymity. There are still some residual systems and formats which may seem odd due to the nature of the adaptation, but we are interested in improving the game so that those become less of an issue.

Notably, there is an option to cheat/adjust any of your stats in the Use Items and Relics menu. If you think of a creative solution for anything in the game, you can use that menu to account for it, but I would also strongly encourage you to post about it on our Discord server so that it can be properly implemented in the game!

Additionally, there is always a "Use a combination of Relics" option to defeat any threat, and this is essentially a cheat button for encounters if you have a specific plan for dealing with them. I would encourage only using it if you have a well thought out plan for dealing with the threat.

